
# Hand Gesture Volume Control 🎛️🖐️  

An AI-powered hand gesture volume control system using **Python, OpenCV, MediaPipe, and Pycaw**. Control system volume with your hand movements!  

## 🚀 Features  
✅ **Real-time hand tracking** with OpenCV & MediaPipe  
✅ **Gesture-based volume control** (Palm open = Adjust volume)  
✅ **Thumb Up/Down detection** for feedback  
✅ **Smooth & responsive control**  

## 🛠️ Technologies Used  
🔹 **Python**  
🔹 **OpenCV** - For computer vision processing  
🔹 **MediaPipe** - For hand tracking  
🔹 **Pycaw** - For controlling system volume  

